					<description><![CDATA[These horrendous attacks in London will make Jewish communities feel unsafe across our country including Newcastle. I want to send solidarity and sympathy to everyone affected, we will stand up to and defeat the agents of violence and bigotry in our country. More Information:    https://x.com/MayorofLondon/status/2049457457093603333 BBC News:  https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/c3ve2nr60xzt &#160; &#160; &#160; &#160;]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h4>These horrendous attacks in London will make Jewish communities feel unsafe across our country including Newcastle.</h4>
<h4>I want to send solidarity and sympathy to everyone affected, we will stand up to and defeat the agents of violence and bigotry in our country.</h4>
<h4>More Information:    <a href="https://x.com/MayorofLondon/status/2049457457093603333">https://x.com/MayorofLondon/status/2049457457093603333</a></h4>
<p><strong>BBC News:</strong>  <strong><a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/c3ve2nr60xzt">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/live/c3ve2nr60xzt</a></strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
