										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">When Lucy Powell MP and Anna Turley MP </span><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">joined me campaigning in Blakelaw  </span><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">we had to pop into Greggs !</span></p>
<p><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"> I went for the doughnuts but Lucy went for the stotties &#8211; which she said reminded her of Manchester Barm Cakes&#8230; anyone know if they are related?</span></p>
