					<description><![CDATA[Some people, and I know Stephen is one, believe politics is about listening to people, standing up for them and strengthening communities Others believe it&#8217;s about vandalism and vile lies. They think they will win over Newcastle with intimidation and attacks. But they are wrong See the Chronicle article:  https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/news/north-east-news/newcastle-labour-councillor-devastated-home-33835161]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h4>Some people, and I know Stephen is one, believe politics is about listening to people, standing up for them and strengthening communities</h4>
<h4>Others believe it&#8217;s about vandalism and vile lies.</h4>
<h4>They think they will win over Newcastle with intimidation and attacks.</h4>
<h4>But they are wrong</h4>
<h4>See the Chronicle article:  <a href="https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/news/north-east-news/newcastle-labour-councillor-devastated-home-33835161">https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/news/north-east-news/newcastle-labour-councillor-devastated-home-33835161</a></h4>
